<sect2>
<title>Introduction to <application>OpenQuicktime</application></title>

<para><application>OpenQuicktime</application> is a small library that handles the Quicktime
file format on most varieties of Unix. Audio and video decoding and
encoding is provided using a plug-in mechanism.</para>

